==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Strait-jacket
<hw>Strait"-jack`et</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A dress of
strong materials for restraining maniacs or those who are violently
delirious. It has long sleeves, which are closed at the ends, confining
the hands, and may be tied behind the back.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Strait-laced</ent>⟦br⟧
